# InspireMe: Quote of the Day Generator (Flask Web App)

## 🎯 Project Overview
Develop a Flask-based web application titled **"InspireMe: Quote of the Day Generator"**, which dynamically displays a new inspirational quote each time the page is refreshed or when the user clicks the **"Get New Quote"** button.

The system stores a predefined list of motivational quotes within the Flask backend and uses **Jinja2 templating** to render them dynamically on the frontend.

Users can also contribute their own quotes through a **Bootstrap modal form**, which are temporarily stored in memory and displayed as part of the rotating list.

---

## 🧩 Features
- Displays a random quote on each page load.
- **"Get New Quote"** button fetches new quotes instantly using AJAX.
- Modal popup for users to submit their own quotes.
- Confirmation page after quote submission.
- Clean, responsive UI built with Bootstrap and minimal CSS.

